 =20

I feel like a pretty popular story=C2=A0of crypto exchange FTX Trading Inc.=
 and its affiliated trading firm Alameda Research=C2=A0is something like =
=E2=80=9CFTX and Alameda=C2=A0looked like=C2=A0extremely lucrative business=
