<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One possibility is that <a href=3D"https://lin=
k.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31488443.258437/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21i=
ZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDQtMjAvYmFua2luZy1nZXRzLWEtYml0LW5=
